<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed">Dear investors,<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"en-IL"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed">I hope this mail finds you well.<span lang=3D"en-IL"><o:p></o:p></sp=
an></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"en-IL"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed">Please find attached an Executive Summary of Q3 2022 activity.<span =
lang=3D"HE" dir=3D"RTL"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed">In addition, you received an additional mail from the fund's adminis=
trator (Tzur) with a link to the following documents:<o:p></o:p></p>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-right:0cm;text-align:left;ms=
o-list:l1 level1 lfo3;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed">
Financial Statements for Q3-2022<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagra=
ph" style=3D"margin-right:0cm;text-align:left;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3;direc=
tion:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed">
Capital Account as of September 30, 2022<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoLis=
tParagraph" style=3D"margin-right:0cm;text-align:left;mso-list:l1 level1 lf=
o3;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed">
Capital Call Notice <o:p></o:p></li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed">A kind reminder that Stardom Ventures will hold its
<u>Annual LP Meeting</u> in Tel Aviv on Dec. 11th at 18:00.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"xmsonormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I</span><span lang=
=3D"en-IL" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">f you haven=92t already, please confi=
rm your attendance and RSVP
<a href=3D"https://www.eventbrite.com/e/stardom-ventures-2022-annual-meetin=
g-tickets-428473675297">
here</a></span>.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><span lang=3D"en-IL"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed">Please let me know if you have any further questions.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed">Best regards,<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:=
embed">Aviran<span lang=3D"en-IL"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" dir=3D"RTL"><span lang=3D"en-IL" dir=3D"LTR"><o:p>&n=
